  "content": "<div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\"><blockquote><p><span>Plunge into the action-packed universe of Capsule Heroes, a unique PvP brawler that blends intense combat with strategic depth, </span><strong>developed by Endless Clouds.</strong></p></blockquote><p data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/introducing-capsule-heroes?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\" class=\"button-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/introducing-capsule-heroes?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=share&amp;action=share\" rel=\"\" class=\"button primary\"><span>Share</span></a></p><div id=\"youtube2-1d06bHl2V2I\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;1d06bHl2V2I&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"Youtube2ToDOM\" class=\"youtube-wrap\"><div class=\"youtube-inner\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/1d06bHl2V2I?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowautoplay=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\"></iframe></div></div><p><span>Capsule Heroes is a F2P </span><em>groundbreaking</em><span> PvP brawler, party up with your friends and participate in a series of game modes from Occupy, to Team Deathmatch to Survival. Choose between a plethora of unique-looking skins and march into combat. Designed for casuals, and those with a competitive spirit.</span></p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!eNKd!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1214feb9-e702-4c98-955e-5e66b961bf94_1920x1080.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!eNKd!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1214feb9-e702-4c98-955e-5e66b961bf94_1920x1080.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!eNKd!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1214feb9-e702-4c98-955e-5e66b961bf94_1920x1080.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!eNKd!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1214feb9-e702-4c98-955e-5e66b961bf94_1920x1080.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!eNKd!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1214feb9-e702-4c98-955e-5e66b961bf94_1920x1080.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!eNKd!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1214feb9-e702-4c98-955e-5e66b961bf94_1920x1080.jpeg\" width=\"1456\" height=\"819\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1214feb9-e702-4c98-955e-5e66b961bf94_1920x1080.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:819,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:318048,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!eNKd!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1214feb9-e702-4c98-955e-5e66b961bf94_1920x1080.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!eNKd!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1214feb9-e702-4c98-955e-5e66b961bf94_1920x1080.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!eNKd!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1214feb9-e702-4c98-955e-5e66b961bf94_1920x1080.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!eNKd!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1214feb9-e702-4c98-955e-5e66b961bf94_1920x1080.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>A subteam inside Endless Clouds has been silently working on Capsule Heroes for the last few months. The initial concept emerged from a game jam we held at the start of the year. The team had so much fun playing the game, and we decided to continue working on it.</p><div data-component-name=\"VideoEmbedPlayer\" id=\"media-b4569ce9-57b3-4e4b-a9a2-3209a0a77506\" class=\"videoScrollTarget-SzB20Y\"><div class=\"videoEmbed-_FycLU\"><div role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Video player\" class=\"with-preview full-width video-player-with-background video-player-wrapper full-width\"><div class=\"video-player video-player video-player-with-background videoPlayer-vlcedM\"><video controlslist=\"nodownload\" poster=\"https://substack-video.s3.amazonaws.com/video_upload/post/132713029/b4569ce9-57b3-4e4b-a9a2-3209a0a77506/transcoded-00001.png?refresh=Thu Jul 10 2025 21:42:43 GMT+0100 (British Summer Time)\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" class=\"video-P2qgwZ\" src=\"blob:https://endlessclouds.substack.com/a21d7905-d3ef-4a08-855b-8d509d75bdfa\"></video><div class=\"pencraft pc-position-absolute pc-reset buttonContainer-tH3LP9 video-player-button\"><button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"r\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft media-XfKJl4 size_md-gCDS3o priority_primary-RfbeYt iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_md-gCDS3o priority_primary-RfbeYt rounded-SYxRdz\" style=\"width: 56px; height: 56px;\"><svg role=\"img\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-label=\"Play\" class=\"videoIcon-pEKkgy\" style=\"stroke: none;\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M3.35866 16C2.58101 16 2 15.4101 2 14.4447V1.55531C2 0.598883 2.58101 0 3.35866 0C3.75196 0 4.10056 0.134078 4.54749 0.393296L15.1575 6.54302C15.9531 7.00782 16.3106 7.39218 16.3106 8C16.3106 8.61676 15.9531 9.00112 15.1575 9.45698L4.54749 15.6067C4.10056 15.8659 3.75196 16 3.35866 16Z\"></path></g></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div><p><span>We plan to have an Alpha Q4 of this year. 10 of you can win an invite if you </span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/CapsuleHeroes/status/1677029812408295431\" rel=\"\">retweet this tweet</a><span>. Good luck! We will also have earlier private tests for active community members ~ so be sure to join </span><a href=\"https://discord.gg/endlessclouds\" rel=\"\">Discord</a><span>.</span></p><p><em>Capsule Heroes will not start with any NFT implementation at the official launch. We want to test it out asap on the public market. We hope to implement them as time passes.</em></p><p><span>You can keep up to date with the latest news on Capsule Heroes by subscribing to this newsletter. Any small developments will be posted on the </span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/CapsuleHeroes\" rel=\"\">Twitter account</a><span>!</span></p><div><hr></div><div data-component-name=\"SubscribeWidget\" class=\"subscribe-widget\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-justifyContent-center pc-reset\"><div class=\"container-IpPqBD\"><form action=\"/api/v1/free?nojs=true\" method=\"post\" class=\"form form-M5sC90\" novalidate=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/end-claim-is-now-live\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_referrer\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/introducing-capsule-heroes\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_referrer\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/introducing-capsule-heroes\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_referrer\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referral_code\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"subscribe-widget\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referring_pub_id\"